                            <comment id="14704043" author="JIRAUSER20507" created="Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:34:10 -0700"  >&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8305746&quot; title=&quot;InitializeEncoding should cache Charset object instead of charset name&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8305746&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8305746&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; may be related. Reverting the commit there does seem to restore the expected &amp;quot;Properties init: Could not determine current working directory.&amp;quot; exception message.</comment>
